reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made, comfortable, and appreciate its soft material, with one noting it's not itchy at all.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars New Faves
items.body: Bought 2. I usually wear a small but bought mediums for an extra oversized look. They are very baggy as I wanted. They are perfect. Well made, soft material, look as pictured (for once) and I will probably buy more! Read more
items.author: JJ Rich

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute and comfy
items.body: I’ve gotten so many compliments on this sweater! Color is great, runs true to size. Perfect to wear with leggings or jeans. Read more
items.author: Kelly

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super soft, great quality sweater!
items.body: For reference: I am 5’5” and 195 lbs. I wear a 38D. I am 47 inches at my widest around my stomach and 46 around my hips. This sweater is very well made and super soft. It fits great all around and the length is perfect. It’s warm, but I don’t think it will be too warm. I also love the color! I got both a M and a L and kept the M. Read more
items.author: Kenna R.

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very Nice Sweater
items.body: I ordered this sweater for my sister's birthday, she loves the color, fit and texture. Read more
items.author: Linda

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great look with any kind of bottom piece
items.body: Super comfortable sweater. Love the color fits well. Loose fit which is perfect for that over sized look. Read more
items.author: The uzamaki clan

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute and would be a favorite except it has a hole
items.body: Love this sweater, I’ve only worn it once, but there is a hole in the shoulder seams. It has a great length, great fit, very cozy but the hole takes down a Star Read more
items.author: Bri Smith

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great quality, cute sweater
items.body: I love this sweater! It has a baggier fit which is what I had wanted and a good weight. It’s a knit material so it’s not really soft but it’s not meant to be. Seam quality is great. I get a ton of compliments when I wear it! Photo of me teaching in it, front right, if you’re curious about length. Read more
items.author: Bloom Chiropractic CO.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Size down
items.body: More oversized than I thought - definitely could have done a small. Giving 5 stars anyway because it’s so soft and the quality is good! Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: 41#khaki, 41#strigreen White, Coblockblack, 41#coffee, Coblockgreen, 41#white, Kblue, 41#red, 41#green, Purple, Coblockapricot, 41#grey, Coblockorange. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
